title: S16 Ep33: Supernatural News/Parashare: Demon & Ghostly Attacks Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Demon & Ghostly Attacks Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Demon & Ghostly Attacks Edition

Dave & Tim, or Tim & Dave, however you prefer them, are back this week with wild stories of Government leaks regarding UFO disclosure and what that could mean, Ancient Artifacts that defy explanation, Bigfoot findings, and a Daughter seemingly shoved to the ground by an unseen force and Granny calls out for help when uncovering what she believes is a demonic presence irritating her grand child.  All that PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind and listener emails and stories of supernatural shenanigans. 

Get your hands on Dave's little package here: www.darknessradio.com/store
